  m_text: "How to Play: \nTo the left is Bob, please say Hello!\nOn the following
    pages, Bob will describe some rules for how he wants his house to be structured.\nIn
    your repository, please make a house for Bob by using folders or files to represent
    parts of the house. Extra parts are okay as long as you do not violate any rules!
    \nIf a room or object is named, please use that exact word in the name!\nSubmit
    your house at the last page when you are done.\nHave fun!"
